headline: New US solar tariffs on Southeast Asia to raise prices, cut profit margins
summary: A new round of U.S. solar panel import tariffs on Southeast Asian producers is expected to raise consumer prices and cut into producer profit margins, but was largely anticipated by industry, analysts...
